name: $system
desc: Returns: An absolute URI which is the code system from which the selected codes come from.

pvardefs.name: pValue

name: $::version
desc: Returns: The version of the code system that the codes are selected from, or the special version '*' for all versions.

pvardefs.desc: The version of the code system that the codes are selected from, or the special version '*' for all versions.

name: $concept
desc: Returns: Specifies a concept to be included or excluded.

desc: Specifies a concept to be included or excluded.

name: $filter
desc: Returns: Select concepts by specify a matching criterion based on the properties (including relationships) defined by the system, or on filters defined by the system. If multiple filters are specified, they SHALL all be true.

name: $addfilter
desc: Select concepts by specify a matching criterion based on the properties (including relationships) defined by the system, or on filters defined by the system. If multiple filters are specified, they SHALL all be true.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Select concepts by specify a matching criterion based on the properties (including relationships) defined by the system, or on filters defined by the system. If multiple filters are specified, they SHALL all be true.

name: $valueSet
desc: Returns: Selects the concepts found in this value set (based on its value set definition). This is an absolute URI that is a reference to ValueSet.url.  If multiple value sets are specified this includes the union of the contents of all of the referenced value sets.
